data.description: Unparalleled lake and mountain views from this well appointed pool home!  Whether you're indoors or outdoors, this property does not disappoint.  Inside, the main living area flows effortlessly for entertaining. It includes such features as custom raised maple cabinetry, granite countertops, plantation shutters and gorgeous over-sized tile flooring for easy care.  Outside you will find plenty of covered patio space and a built-in barbecue area/bar with seating for 6 or more.  At night the pool glows with LED lighting and accent lighting throughout the yard.  Loads of parking on both sides of the home and at the end of a quiet south-side street.  Come see it for yourself and fall in love!
